Barfield's security.

371
00:19:06,278 --> 00:19:08,747
The men involved in the hanging
have all been segregated

372
00:19:08,814 --> 00:19:12,751
for the past six months
and remain in secure cells.

373
00:19:12,818 --> 00:19:15,310
Am I right in assuming
that during cell association

374
00:19:15,388 --> 00:19:18,085
on the night of the hanging, all
the cell doors were kept open?

375
00:19:18,157 --> 00:19:19,625
Yes, which means
that Anthony Kelly

