he wouldn't have been,

388
00:19:50,756 --> 00:19:52,247
but there was no alternative.

389
00:19:52,324 --> 00:19:54,520
So you admit
that by an administrative error

390
00:19:54,593 --> 00:19:56,585
you placed a young
and vulnerable boy at risk?

391
00:19:56,662 --> 00:19:58,631
No.
I admit no such thing.

392
00:19:59,865 --> 00:20:01,231
Good.

393
00:20:06,372 --> 00:20:08,170
I believe if there was
any possible inference

394
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,918
that the present conditions
at Barfield might be used

395
00:20:09,942 --> 00:20:12,605
in Anthony Kelly's defense,
if any negligence...

